Aisha Patel was stuck in analysis paralysis. She knew she wanted to launch a sustainability consulting practice but couldn't decide on positioning, pricing, or even a name.

After using InstantCompany, she had five strong brand options, a clear positioning statement, and a pricing framework that suggested retainer-based packages. She picked GreenLeaf Consulting and never looked back.

"The pricing model was spot-on," Aisha explains. "I would have undercharged by 40% without the AI analysis. It gave me the confidence to price for the value I deliver."

GreenLeaf Consulting hit $10K MRR within six months of launch.
